Method.РазложитьСтрокуВМассивПодстрок.Description=Razbivaet Row To neskolko Rows By ukazannomu razdelitelyu. Separator mozhet imet lyubuyu Length.\nV sluchayakh, kogda razdelitelem yavlyaetsya String From Single simvola, T Dont ispolzuetsya Parameter SokrashchatNepechataemyeSimvoly,\nrekomenduetsya Use funktsiyu Platform StrRazdelit.
Method.РазложитьСтрокуВМассивПодстрок.Example.Description=StrokovyeFunktsiiKlientServer.SplitStringIntoSubstringsArray(",Single,,dva,", ",")\n- vozvratit Array From 5 Items, tri From kotorykh  - pustye\: "", "Single", "", "dva", "";\nStrokovyeFunktsiiKlientServer.SplitStringIntoSubstringsArray(",Single,,dva,", ",", Istina)\n- vozvratit Array From dvukh Items\: "Single", "dva";\nStrokovyeFunktsiiKlientServer.SplitStringIntoSubstringsArray(" Single   dva  ", " ")\n- vozvratit Array From dvukh Items\: "Single", "dva";\nStrokovyeFunktsiiKlientServer.SplitStringIntoSubstringsArray("")\n- vozvratit Empty Array;\nStrokovyeFunktsiiKlientServer.SplitStringIntoSubstringsArray("",,Lozh)\n- vozvratit Array C odnim elementom\: ""(Page String);\nStrokovyeFunktsiiKlientServer.SplitStringIntoSubstringsArray("", " ")\n- vozvratit Array C odnim elementom\: "" (Page String).
