Method.СтрокаСЧисломДляЛюбогоЯзыка.Example.Description=Presentation Table\:\n\nLang | Zero | One             | Two            | Few               | Many                  | Other\n\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\nru   |      | XX1 / X11       |                | XX2-XX4 / X12-X14 | XX0, XX5-XX9, X11-X14 | drobnye\nCard.|      | ostalsya %1 den |                | ostalos %1 dnya   | ostalos %1 dney      | ostalos %1 dnya\n|      | vizhu %1 rybu    |                | vizhu %1-V ryb     | vizhu %5 ryb           | vizhu %1 ryby\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nru   |      |                 |                |                   |                       | Edit Objects\nOrd. |      |                 |                |                   |                       | %1-y den\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nen   |      | To 1           |                |                   |                       | ostalnoe\nCard.|      | Left %1 day     |                |                   |                       | Left %1 days\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nen   |      | XX1 / X11       | XX2 / X12      | XX3 / X13         |                       | ostalnoe\nOrd. |      | %1st day        | %1nd day       | %1rd day          |                       | %1th day.\nCard. - Cardinal - Kolichestvennoe;\nOrd.  - Ordinal  - Poryadkovoe;\nX - lyubaya tsifra;\n- krome.\nStroka \= StrokovyeFunktsiiKlientServer.StringWithNumberForAnyLanguage(\nNStr("ru\=';ostalsya %1 den;;ostalos %1 dnya;ostalos %1 dney;ostalos %1 dnya';\n|en\=';Left %1 day;;;;Left %1 days'"),\n0.05,, "ChDTs\=1");
